\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
This is the most concrete physical prediction.
 A squeezed vacuum at fixed 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{k}$
\end_inset

 generates correlations between modes 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{k}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $-\mathbf{k}$
\end_inset

