\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C(\mathbf{k},-\mathbf{k})=1+\left|\frac{\langle a(\mathbf{k})a(-\mathbf{k})\rangle}{\langle a^{\dagger}(\mathbf{k})a(\mathbf{k})\rangle}\right|^{2}>1
\]

\end_inset

This is distinct from the usual HBT effect which correlates 
\begin_inset Formula $(\mathbf{k},\mathbf{k})$
\end_inset

